# Keep the build context small. Images COPY only the dirs they need (the Trends image
# common/ + google_trends_api/; the API image web/ source + api/), so everything else is
# noise — and data/ can get large. node_modules/ is excluded so a host (macOS) install is
# never copied over the in-image `npm ci` (native-binary mismatch).
.git/
.claude/
data/
downloads/
terraform/
node_modules/
web/dist/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
